TOML
====

Parser for TOML, https://github.com/mojombo/toml.

Usage
-----

::

    data = toml.loads(string)

Where::

    --help|-h           Show this help message and exit.
    --version           Show version number and exit.

Long description.

Dependencies
------------

Any OS.
Python 3.3.
See requirements.txt for Python packages.

Install
-------

::

    pip install toml

Known Problems
--------------

Doesn't work. Not remotely finished.

Alternatives
------------

Many listed on https://github.com/mojombo/toml.

Thanks
------

Tom, I suppose.

Hacking
-------

To hack on this project, first install development dependencies::

    pip install -f requirements-dev.txt

Then get the source code into your virtualenv::

    python setup.py develop

And run tests::

    make test

The included Makefile has other useful targets, check it out.


